"Excellent" Megatron boomed, as he accompanied them in the elevator
towards the lower end of the Stunticons ship. The door opened to a
chime, as they walked out, towards the large stack of cubes. "If you
need to recharge, now is a good time." Megatron suggested, as he picked
up a large armfull, and dumped them into a square slot in the wall. The
heat from the slot was more intense than the rest of the room that held
the engine.
